dataIdInfo.idPurp: Policia_Locs contains coordinates for the Comandancia de Policia and Academia de Policia Municipal in addition to 21 fictitious police stations in Ciudad Juarez, Mexico.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: Policia_Locs contains coordinates for the Comandancia de Policia and Academia de Policia Municipal in addition to 21 fictitious police stations in Ciudad Juarez, Mexico. The Comandancia de Policia and Academia de Policia Municipal were digitized from imagery and their locations are correct. The other police stations are purposefully fictitious due to the ongoing security situation in Mexico.
